00:20:02,684 --> 00:20:04,945
- Just a little bit what?

402
00:20:04,981 --> 00:20:06,266
Oh, come on, say it, Larry.

403
00:20:06,301 --> 00:20:08,247
A little what?

404
00:20:08,282 --> 00:20:09,152
Greedy?

