00:20:10,786 --> 00:20:14,088
Greed, it's just a word, Larry.

406
00:20:14,122 --> 00:20:17,252
An ordinary word for ordinary people.

407
00:20:17,286 --> 00:20:18,156
Come here.

408
00:20:22,605 --> 00:20:24,552
Look at them all down there.

409
00:20:24,586 --> 00:20:26,707
