412
00:20:31,504 --> 00:20:35,224
One hour lunch, go home, eat dinner, watch TV,

413
00:20:35,259 --> 00:20:38,527
maybe have a bowl of ice cream.

414
00:20:38,562 --> 00:20:40,996
