417
00:20:50,242 --> 00:20:52,640
We're not like them, Larry.

418
00:20:52,676 --> 00:20:55,074
We are not ordinary.

419
00:20:55,108 --> 00:20:55,979
No, sir.

420
00:20:57,230 --> 00:20:59,490
What we are, what we do,

421
00:21:00,567 --> 00:21:03,696
